{"tid":418308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【傘運三周年】黃台仰赴倫敦 與居英港人同紀念","createTime":"2017-09-29T12:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T12:55:15.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92b93cf37c0b85fb85c03be6ac312999a29eef2c","tid":418308,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"【傘運三周年】黃台仰赴倫敦 與居英港人同紀念<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170929&amp;guid=57268544&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170929%26guid%3D57268544%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=dY%2BwcgPoOsdsY2SB3VcuJ%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=12165b6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170929%26guid%3D57268544%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=21d93d85\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170929&amp;guid=57268544&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n特約記者林景輝英國倫敦報道】<br />\n今日是雨傘運動三周年，本土民主前線發言人黃台仰及成員李東昇前赴英國倫敦，聯同約十名居英港人出席紀念活動。<br />\n<br />\n黃台仰、李東昇及約十名居英港人，於國會大廈外舉起象徵雨傘運動的黃傘及「Freedom in Hong Kong」橫額，紀念雨傘運動三周年。他於紀錄活動中表示，雨傘運動改變了他的一生，他因此投身社運，成立本土民前線。他指經歷銅鑼灣書店店主被擄、立法會議員被取消資格、多名示威者被判囚、大學言論自由受威脅，顯示中國破壞了「一國兩制」承諾，證明共產黨恐懼自由及民主，支持民主的年輕人受到前所未有的危機。他指這是「民主與極權、自由與壓迫、文明與野蠻的戰爭」，希望國際多作關注。<br />\n<br />\n前港督彭定康亦有留言支持，他稱國際社會繼續支持香港法治與民主發展實屬重要，同時要求中國實踐其承諾。他會支持為民主發聲的社運人士，明日亦會在牛津大學與香港眾志成員林淳軒會面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170928/large/1506608295_ceec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170928%2Flarge%2F1506608295_ceec.png&h=71366371&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4fd3e112b169fa756d7762ea0bdb3c8a04ba300","tid":418308,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"dont升咁撚型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0088b0e7e54e0328a563161eae169aa38aa10f4c","tid":418308,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}